(Summary) Tj
T*
(Ecology is a valuable part of Biology. Students perform better when they understand) Tj
T*
(ecosystems, food chains, and environmental balance, learn from examples such as showing) Tj
T*
(how a change in one species affects others, and deliberately avoid mistakes like) Tj
T*
(treating organisms as if they live independently of habitat. Regular practice built) Tj
T*
(around ecosystem and population questions makes the topic easier to remember and apply.) Tj
T*
